-# About Flex
- content_for :about do
  %h2 What is Flex?
  %p
    Flex is a free platform-as-a-service for new and existing JBoss, Java EE6 and PHP applications. Provision cloud resources, deploy, manage, monitor and auto-scale applications from a single, easy-to-use interface.

